snippet.title: SunshineBaby
snippet.description:
Raelynn is our SunshineBaby! Raelynn is our epileptic, quadriplegic, beautiful daughter. We started fostering her when she was 17 months old, and adopted her when she was 5 years old. She's had many, MANY trials along the way, but we're thankful that God has a plan for her, and that even now, she's fulfilling God's purpose for her. There's always hope even when life seems hopeless.

We post videos of Raelynn's seizures, surgeries, assistive medical technologies, and life with disabilities. With every upload, we hope that you'll be inspired and encouraged in your life as well!

Back when we were fostering her, we couldn't use Raelynn's name online. So when we started this YouTube channel (which only had private videos at first), we called her our "Sunshine" Baby because her name is Raelynn, and she's a beautiful Ray of Sunshine!
